\par\plain {\f4\fs28\b1\i0\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>Guido: <!$Scr_Cs::6>}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>"I don't know nothing about this chick, except that Evan is nuts about her and calls her his girlfriend. That's the first time I ever heard him call someone's girlfriend. It all happened so fast. I haven't even met her yet."<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
