\par\plain {\f4\fs28\b1\i0\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>Roxanne: <!$Scr_Cs::6>}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>"Look at her, trying to look like one of us. She'll never be one of us. Look, she even bought a fucking book to read."<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
