\par\plain {\f4\fs28\b1\i0\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>Roxanne: <!$Scr_Cs::6>}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8221\'94He should be with you, Patti. I know it, you know it, everyone knows it. Right, Guido?"<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f4\fs28\b1\i0\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>Guido: <!$Scr_Cs::6>}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>"I ain't saying nothing. I want no part of all your drama stuff."<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f4\fs28\b1\i0\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>Patti: <!$Scr_Cs::6>}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>"Shush! Here they come."<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f4\fs28\b1\i0\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::6>}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2>"It's nice to meet you all."<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Ps::4>Tone:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Curious, Somber, Wounded, Reflective<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Action Tags/Dialogue Tags:<!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::7>}
\par\pard\plain \tx235\tx720\li936\fi-212\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch \ls5\ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf8 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf8 When introducing Sarah, aware of her nervousness, Evan stands back with Sarah several feet and quickly introduces Patti, Roxanne, Guido, and a few other friends who play no vital role in the story. The reason he stands back is so that no one feels an obligation to handshake or hug. The game starts immediately after the introduction. Guido and Evan head for the field.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf8 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf8 Guido says, Evan. He's all about "chemistry." In a mocking tone. Because Guido is not a romantic and puts no value on the concept of romantic chemistry.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf8 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf8 Patti is reflective and serene during this scene, even though inside, she is hurting.}
